de.jpdigital.owlapisimplex

Class OwlApiSimplexUtils

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.jpdigital.owlapisimplex.OwlApiSimplexUtils

  • public class OwlApiSimplexUtils
extends Object
    A helper class for owlapi-simplex-utils. Used to pass the necessary instances of classes from the OWL API to other classes. Also provides factory methods for some classes provided by owlapi-simplex-utils.
    Author:
    Jens Pelzetter
